  "texts": [
    "Proposed human motion intention prediction modelIn this research work, a novel human motion intention prediction mechanism is constructed using the multimodal data and deep learning approach.",
    "The major goal of the implemented human motion intention prediction model is to understand human behaviors to achieve higher efficiency in human-to-robot interaction tasks.",
    "Phase 1: In the initial phase, inputs like EEG and EMG signals are gathered from the benchmark resources.",
    "Then, the collected input signals are converted into spectrogram images and fed into the AH-CNN-LSTM-based human motion intention prediction phase.",
    "The developed AH-CNN-LSTM-based motion intention prediction model using data is designed by integrating the CNN mechanism with LSTM."
  ],
